sentences: Chaz Bear (born Chazwick Bradley Bundick; November 7, 1986), known professionally as Toro y Moi, is an American singer, songwriter, record producer, and graphic designer.
His music has taken on many forms since he began recording, but he is often identified with the rise of the chillwave movement in 2010 and 2011.
Chaz Bundick was born on November 7, 1986, in Columbia, South Carolina, to a Filipino mother and an African American father.
Bundick graduated from the University of South Carolina in spring of 2009 with a bachelor's degree in graphic design.
